<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.4">
<l>mēvi niṉṟu toḻuvār viṉaipōka mēvumpirāṉ</l>
<l>tūviyam puḷḷu ṭaiyā ṉaṭalāḻiya māṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>nāviya lālicai mālaika ḷēttinaṇ ṇappeṟṟēṉ</l>
<l>āviyeṉ ṉāviyai yāṉaṟiyēṉceyta vāṟṟaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who dwells so that the karma of those who constantly dwell [and] worship goes,</l>
<l>he who possessesthe feathered pretty bird, the lord with the deadly discus,</l>
<l>praising him in a musical garland with the property of [my] tongue I have obtained that he approaches.</l>
<l>I don’t know the way he does to the soul of me who has a soul.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
